# Day 44 – LinkedIn Profile Optimizer

##  Project Overview
Built an interactive **LinkedIn Profile Optimizer** that analyzes a user's LinkedIn profile and provides personalized recommendations to improve visibility, personal branding, and recruiter appeal.

##  Features
- LinkedIn profile analysis
- Profile report card with scores
- Headline optimization suggestions
- About section improvements
- Experience optimization
- Skills recommendations
- Before vs After comparison
- 7-Day LinkedIn activation plan
- Shareable summary card
- Responsive UI with local storage

##  Technologies Used
- HTML5
- CSS3
- JavaScript (Vanilla)
- Local Storage

##  Key Learnings
- LinkedIn profile optimization
- Personal branding fundamentals
- Keyword optimization for recruiter search
- UI/UX design principles
- Frontend application development

